  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automate a team of robots to gather resources, reshape terrain, and scale up factories on a procedurally generated alien world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a procedural world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every game you are exploring a different planet, with a different set of resources and biomes that present unique challenge. You start able to only see a small area, but as you progress you build out a radio network and unlock more of the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/133369ab56f92a64bcf550b6370fa677.poster.avif?t=1766036230\" width=544 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/133369ab56f92a64bcf550b6370fa677.webm?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/133369ab56f92a64bcf550b6370fa677.mp4?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect resources</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanding your colony requires ever increasing quantity of resources. Luckily, the planet you're on is ripe with them to find and use. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/f0d92090bf7335228e582bdb569ee3d1.poster.avif?t=1766036230\" width=544 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/f0d92090bf7335228e582bdb569ee3d1.webm?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/f0d92090bf7335228e582bdb569ee3d1.mp4?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Programming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anything you can do you can automate. It becomes a necessity as your colony grows larger, and recipes get more complex. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/497e41e30e8725c7ac446c7df5b11544.poster.avif?t=1766036230\" width=544 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/497e41e30e8725c7ac446c7df5b11544.webm?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/497e41e30e8725c7ac446c7df5b11544.mp4?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Single-player colony-builder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Automatable robots and factories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Procedurally generated voxel world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Mutable terrain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An easy-to-learn visual scripting language</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sharable scripts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fog-of-war and power mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Crafting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trucks for long-distance transit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trees that grow, die, and can be farmed</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automate a team of robots to gather resources, reshape terrain, and scale up factories on a procedurally generated alien world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a procedural world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every game you are exploring a different planet, with a different set of resources and biomes that present unique challenge. You start able to only see a small area, but as you progress you build out a radio network and unlock more of the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/133369ab56f92a64bcf550b6370fa677.poster.avif?t=1766036230\" width=544 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/133369ab56f92a64bcf550b6370fa677.webm?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/133369ab56f92a64bcf550b6370fa677.mp4?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect resources</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanding your colony requires ever increasing quantity of resources. Luckily, the planet you're on is ripe with them to find and use. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/f0d92090bf7335228e582bdb569ee3d1.poster.avif?t=1766036230\" width=544 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/f0d92090bf7335228e582bdb569ee3d1.webm?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/f0d92090bf7335228e582bdb569ee3d1.mp4?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Programming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anything you can do you can automate. It becomes a necessity as your colony grows larger, and recipes get more complex. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/497e41e30e8725c7ac446c7df5b11544.poster.avif?t=1766036230\" width=544 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/497e41e30e8725c7ac446c7df5b11544.webm?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/497e41e30e8725c7ac446c7df5b11544.mp4?t=1766036230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Single-player colony-builder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Automatable robots and factories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Procedurally generated voxel world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Mutable terrain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An easy-to-learn visual scripting language</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sharable scripts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fog-of-war and power mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Crafting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trucks for long-distance transit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trees that grow, die, and can be farmed</p></li></ul>",
